snippet.title: Abbey Sharp
snippet.description: Abbey Sharp is a Registered Dietitian (RD), an avid food writer and blogger, a TV and radio personality, a food brand ambassador, a passionate home cook, a food event hostess, and the founder of Abbey's Kitchen Inc. Her YouTube channel features her top healthy recipes, nutrition myths, kitchen tips, fun foodie adventures, celebrity chef interviews, and so much more!
